E-08 FORECAST DATE IS INVALID!
E-09 ENTER FORM A OR B!
E-10 ENTER USER PART NO.!
E-11 UPDATE CODE SHOULD BE BLANK OR 0!
E-12 DATA DOES NOT EXIST!
E-13 DATA WAS ALREADY CANCELED!
E-14 DATE IS NOT CORRECT!
E-15 DATE(FROM-TO) IS NOT CORRECT!
E-16 ENTER FORECAST QTY!
E-17 DATE IS INVALID!
E-18 FORECAST QTY IS INVALID!
E-19 FORECAST DATE(MONTH) IS INVALID!
